flowchart TD
    A[Create or update JOATU request/offer/agreement] --> B[Default privacy private]
    B --> C{Actor chooses public visibility?}
    C -- No --> D[Remain private or participant-scoped]
    C -- Yes --> E[Run public publishing agreement gate]
    E --> F{Agreement + authorization valid?}
    F -- No --> G[Reject public transition]
    F -- Yes --> H[Persist public JOATU record]

    D --> I[Policy scope allows creator or participant access]
    H --> J[Policy scope allows public discovery]

    subgraph JOATU Records
      RQ[Request]
      OF[Offer]
      AG[Agreement]
    end

    RQ --> A
    OF --> A
    AG --> A

    subgraph Read Rules
      K[Unrelated authenticated users]
      L[Creators and participants]
      M[Stewards and managers]
    end

    J --> K
    I --> L
    I --> M
    J --> M
